# Hand Gesture Recognition using KNN

A real-time Hand Gesture Recognition system built using **OpenCV, MediaPipe, and K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN)**.  
The system detects hand landmarks from a webcam feed, trains a KNN model on collected gesture data, and predicts gestures in real time.

---

## Features

- Real-time hand tracking using MediaPipe
- Custom dataset collection
- KNN-based gesture classification
- Live gesture prediction using webcam
- Lightweight and fast model
- Easy to extend with new gestures

